      • display

        public void display()
        displays a Card's rank and suit. Ex-8S which is the eight of spades

      • getRankValue

        public int getRankValue()
        gives a card a value based on its rank. The higher the rank, the higher value the card has. This allows the program to later be able to compare two cards, to see which has a higher rank.
        Returns:
        int- returns the assigned value of the card based on its rank

      • getCardValue

        public int getCardValue()
        gives each card a value which is how much that card is worth. Ace has a value of 1 and tens, kings, queens, and jacks all have values of 10
        Returns:
        int- returns the integer value the card is worth
